caption.text:
[Edisi Menolak Lupa] 
4 years ago, I was trying so hard to be accepted by my new society by actively involved in any student activities (trying to become ketang is one of which). Some of them were working yet most of them weren't. All of this measures were self-inflicted wound, therefore I barely belief on my own justifications. 
Yet, these freak(ing awesome) guys emerged during my lowest point. Being among these guys prompted me to realize that I didn't need to work very hard to be accepted. It's just about to be in the right place with the right insane friends. Thank you, it would be unnecessary to write more about how I am grateful to have a chance to be with this guys, because words will never be enough. *I barely write my thoughts on social media, but this one is worth it.

Taken by: @septianalamsyah
